data.description:
Welcome to your dream mid-century modern retreat in the heart of Port Orange, Florida! This architectural masterpiece seamlessly blends the charm of the past with the modern conveniences of today. Located in an established neighborhood, this home exudes character and style, offering a unique living experience.A huge bonus to this property is that is offers a full in-law suite. Could be an income potential or just a bonus for family coming down to visit. As you step inside, be prepared to be captivated by the open and airy design, characteristic of mid-century modern homes. Sunlight streams through large windows, highlighting the clean lines and thoughtful design elements throughout the property. The spacious living areas are perfect for entertaining, with a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen.

One of the standout features of this home is its commitment to sustainability, boasting a state-of-the-art
solar panel system on the roof. Embrace eco-friendly living while enjoying the cost savings that come with harnessing the power of the Florida sun.

For nature enthusiasts and fishing aficionados, the proximity to Rose Bay offers unparalleled access to some of the best fishing spots in Volusia County. Spend your weekends casting a line and soaking in the breathtaking views of the bay.

When it's time to unwind, take a short drive to the beach and feel the sand between your toes. The convenience of having Tanger Outlets nearby means that excellent shopping options are just a stone's throw away. From fashion to home decor, indulge in retail therapy without venturing too far from your mid-century oasis.

This property is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Immerse yourself in the charm of an established neighborhood while relishing the modern amenities and sustainable features that make this residence truly exceptional. Your mid-century modern masterpiece awaits - seize the opportunity to call it home!
